review.reviewBody: Spicy salmon sashimi is fresh and the 2 different spicy sauces give the dish a unique contrast in taste. Yummy!
Awesome, way and beyond any other Sushi around here.  Party tray is fabulous, each flavour is distinctive and delicious.

The 1st time we ordered everything was fresh and delicious and we were so happy as we just moved to South Surrey and miss our usual
spot in Van. The 2nd time was not the same :( Most items were mushy, made clumsy and did not taste as fresh.  Bummer...consistency is so crucial -- and hard to come by thesedays.
I ordered to add cream cheese on Tempura Double Yam Tempura Roll, which cost $2, but it arrived with nothing
